data.description: The seller has increased the incentive for the buyer to $15,000 with a full price offer!!! It can be used for closing cost or to buy down points or both!!! Welcome home to this gorgeous 5 bedroom 4 bath home featuring a large bonus room in Avendell Subdivision located in the prestigious Wren School district - this home has it all. There is a large guest bedroom downstairs with a walk-in closet and full bathroom that is perfect for an in-law suite or a home-away-from home for your guests. Entertaining is a pleasure with a formal living and dining room as well as a spacious kitchen that opens up to the family room with a gas fireplace that features a heat-a-lator and thermostat. The kitchen boasts a large island, butler's pantry, staggered cabinets and quartz countertops. There is a beautiful staircase that leads to an open loft with immediate access to the master suite, a Jack and Jill suite, a second guest bedroom suite, a bonus room and a large, conveniently located laundry room. The master includes a sitting area, dual closets, dual vanitys, a garden tub and a separate shower. The bonus room has access to the second story balcony and amazing views.  The large two car garage and oversized paved driveway make parking convenient and easy. This home features a large deck on the back of the home overlooking a sloping backyard that leads down to a creek. This home also has  radon fan in the attic. The Avendell community has a clubhouse and a lazy river with a pool for those hot summer days. This is a must see for any buyer!!!
